启动，德黑兰机场航班取消，原油黄金大涨，目前情况如何？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b9bae6f24bb5ff93e357db35c52f570e_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "102 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653425193"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrOnZuKSq3Z9WEAMaCTEwNzQ4MzQ0MSD16oexBjAAOEBABnIJNjUzNDI1MTkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1713521326.789421", "card_id": "Q_653416702", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "李想称「磷酸铁锂电池对增程是个灾难、 NVH 差到崩溃」但在 L6 上使用了这种电池，如何理解？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-2cfd82f45f7419d88272a0b5835c4f01_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "101 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/653416702"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IrOnZuKSq3Z9WEAMaCTEwNzQ4MTU3OSDJsIexBjAAOCtAB3IJNjUzNDE2NzAyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1713521326.789767", "card_id": "Q_653411685", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 55}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "4 月 19 日全天震荡调整：沪指缩量跌 0.29%，油气、低空经济概念股集体走强，如何看待今日 A 股？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "凤凰网财经讯 4 月 19 日，市场全天震荡调整，创业板指领跌，沪指相对偏强。截至收盘，沪指跌 0.29%，深成指跌 1.04%，创业板指跌 1.76%。沪深两市今日成交额 8603 亿，较上个交易日缩量 893 亿。 盘面上，低空经济概念股反复活跃，深城交、安达维尔、万丰奥威、中信海直等 10 余股涨停。周期股早盘走强，其中油气股领涨，潜能恒信、通源石油、贝肯能源、准油股份涨停；磷化工概念股表现活跃，川金诺、湖北宜化、鲁北化工涨停；航运股震荡走强，兴通股份、海油发展、凤凰航运涨停。下跌方面，半导体板块陷入调整，芯源微等多股跌超 5%。 总体上个股跌多涨少，全市场超 3500 只个股下跌。板块方面，油气、磷